{
  "stem": "24885.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yom Kipper-- and we still fasted then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about 1 or 2 o'clock in if afternoon, and the doors opened up and there were the Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was a Hasid then, with the white kittle, and with beards and so on, some with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took the horse and walked out so I can talk to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It gave me a passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] The-- the rabbi said to me, he said, be strong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Survive.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And take nekama.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nekama.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nekama.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Hebrew-- take revenge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a little bit of more than this, but I went into the camp and I told my brothers and everybody, I says, look, there's no reason to fast or do anything.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now let's go and eat and see that we can survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no use to punish yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I told them [CRYING] this, I never forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A picture like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Elie Wiesel was in [NON-ENGLISH] a few years ago, and I told my story about this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[CRYING] From then on, we knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything in our area, from what I understand now, went to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day they came in-- and there was a private company from Leipzig, to disinfect the German barracks, and I was assigned to help him, to shown him around and help him carry the canisters and whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he was all done, he said to me in German, he said, Hersh, I make it for you very easy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stay here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] You'll be gassed right here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This great big German guy, civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
